title: 76 different I-Doser doses, decrypted for SBaGen
description:
This torrent contains 76 different types of doses from I-Doser, decrypted and converted to SBaGen format. Normally, they try to make you pay for EVERY TIME you want to use a dose (perhaps they\&#039;re aiming to simulate the full experience of drug addiction), but I am providing them to you in a format which requires only cross-platform open-source software rather than their Windows-only proprietary player, and which, needless to say, can be used any number of times.
